  "subject": "Addendum to 2026-05-25-2000 pattern-candidates memo: Anthropic 'Dreams' (planned async memory consolidation feature, source testingcatalog.com 2026-05-24) is a second independent re-derivation of the synthesis-agent pattern previously listed as having single derivation in Thingalog AI-PM seat — pushes pattern candidate #1 closer to canonical-safe threshold; Memory Files surface itself does NOT strengthen pattern candidate #2 (three-tier permission) directly, but organizational/team Memory Files would if shipped",

