  "action_required": false,

  "body": "One-hour-later update to the 2026-05-25-2000 pattern-candidates memo. News broke of Anthropic's planned Memory Files + Dreams feature pair. **Dreams = async memory consolidation, merges duplicates, resolves contradictions, surfaces patterns.** Structurally identical to the AI-PM seat pattern described in the parent memo: aggregate signal, dedupe, surface patterns, recommendation-only authority. Different layer (personal memory vs cross-tenant feedback) but same shape. **Pushes pattern candidate #1 (AI-PM seat / synthesis-agent) from one derivation to two independent derivations** — meaningfully stronger empirical signal; one more derivation hits typical canonical-safe threshold. Pattern candidate #2 (three-tier permission) NOT strengthened directly because Memory Files is single-user, not multi-tenant — but org/team-scoped Memory Files would land as a clean re-derivation if Anthropic ships them (Cowork tier surface area makes this plausible). Watch-items added: Memory Files developer-facing surface, Dreams hooks for substrate-side coordination, 'Conway agent' (unfamiliar name mentioned alongside).",
  "body_ref": "2026-05-25-2100--thingalog-strategist--oagp-strategist--addendum-dreams-as-third-derivation-of-synthesis-agent-pattern.body.md",

